
Apache::Wombat - a mod_perl servlet server
==========================================

Apache::Wombat is a Perl Apache module that embeds a Wombat servlet
engine inside Apache.

The web site for Apache::Wombat is located at
<http://wombat.sourceforge.net/>.

To view installation and configuration instructions, look in the docs
subdirectory.

For comments, questions, bug reports etc, join the mailing list for
Wombat users by visiting
<http://lists.sourceforge.net/lists/listinfo/wombat-users>.

